            "text": "<span class='text-muted' style='font-size:0.9em;'>(Urdu not available - English Translation)</span><br><br>Yahya related to me from Malik that he had heard that Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \"Trade with the property of orphans and then it will not be eaten away by zakat.\"",
