            "text": "<span class='text-muted' style='font-size:0.9em;'>(Urdu not available - English Translation)</span><br><br>said that the sahabah of Allah's Messenger (SAW) slept, then got up and offered salah without making ablution.\r\n[Ahmed13943, Abu Dawud 201, Muslim 376]",
