            "text": "<span class='text-muted' style='font-size:0.9em;'>(Urdu not available - English Translation)</span><br><br>reported that the Prophet (SAW) said, \"When a dog laps a vessel wash it seven times, rubbing it with earth the first or the last time. If a cat puts its\r\nmouth into a vessel wash it once.\"\r\n[Ahmed9516, 9936, Bukhari 172, Muslim 279, Abu Dawud 71, 72, Nisai 83, Muslim 364]",
