            "text": "<span class='text-muted' style='font-size:0.9em;'>(Urdu not available - English Translation)</span><br><br>The Apostle of Allah (peace_be_upon_him) said: No one of you should make water in his bath and then wash himself there (after urination). \r\n\r\nThe version of Ahmad has: Then performs ablution there, for evil thoughts come from it.",
