            "hadithnumber": 1359,
            "arabicnumber": 1359,
            "text": "<span class='text-muted' style='font-size:0.9em;'>(Urdu not available - English Translation)</span><br><br>My father said, \"Allah's Apostle said, 'Whoever prays the two cool prayers ('Asr and Fajr) will go to Paradise.' \"",
