            "text": "<span class='text-muted' style='font-size:0.9em;'>(Urdu not available - English Translation)</span><br><br>narrated that Allah's Messenger (SAW) said, \"Salat ul-wusta is the Salah of Asr.\"\r\n[Ahmed 3716, Muslim 628, Ibn e Majah 686]",
